<knowl mode="exercise" xmlns="https://spatext.clontz.org" version="0.2">
  <intro>
    <p>
      For each statement, determine whether the trig function is positive or negative
      and whether it is increasing or decreasing on that quadrant.
    </p>
  </intro>

  <knowl>
    <content>
      <p>1. In Quadrant {{tasks.0.quadrant}}, <m>{{tasks.0.fname}}</m> is (positive/negative) and (increasing/decreasing).</p>
    </content>
    <outtro>
      <p>Answer: <m>{{tasks.0.fname}}</m> is <m>{{tasks.0.sign}}</m> and <m>{{tasks.0.mono}}</m> in Quadrant {{tasks.0.quadrant}}.</p>
    </outtro>
  </knowl>

